sequenceDiagram
  actor U as 用户
  participant W as Web
  participant A as API/BFF
  participant O as AI Orchestrator
  participant C as Context Service
  participant M as Model Gateway
  participant V as Validator
  U->>W: 选中文字/点击实体
  W->>A: POST InteractionEvent(uiVersion)
  A-->>W: 202 interactionId
  W->>A: GET SSE events
  A->>O: start workflow
  O->>O: minimum-update planning
  O->>C: retrieve current article context
  C-->>O: allowed units/source IDs
  par generate slots
    O->>M: background task
    O->>M: situation task
    O->>M: thought task
  end
  M-->>O: structured candidates
  O->>V: deterministic/semantic validation
  V-->>O: pass/repair/unavailable
  O-->>A: semantic block events
  A-->>W: slot.start/block/commit
  W-->>U: only update matching uiVersion slots
  O-->>A: scene.commit / interaction.completed
